LINE.Text: UN PEACEKEEPING COMPLETES JOB IN COTE D'IVOIRE
PEACEKEEPING IN COTE D'IVOIRE UNOCI was established in 2004 under UN resolution 1528 to monitor and support the peace agreement signed by the Ivorian parties a year earlier.

UNOCI protected civilians, enabled inclusive political dialogue and supported the Ivorian Government in the
disarmament, demobilization and reintegration (DDR) of former combatants.
